orms precise hand and arm movements, lifting her arms above her head, then framing her face and chest. The red vehicle remains parked to her right, its black grille, Cadillac crest, and vertical light design clearly visible. In closer views, she turns her head and poses with one hand under her chin, her pink eye makeup and jewelry visible, while the red SUV fills the background.\n\nThe scene changes again to a rooftop or elevated urban lot with a city skyline and mountains in the distance. An orange Cadillac sedan is parked behind a woman in a cream blazer. She repeats a poised hand gesture near her chin, then moves out of view, leaving the orange car centered against the city backdrop. The image flips upside down for a stylized moment: two adults in light-colored outfits stand beside the orange sedan with its doors open. The car’s orange body and dark roof glass dominate as the view passes closely over it.\n\nLarge white capital letters appear across the orange car scene: “BE VIBRANT.” Two people are at the open doors. On the left, a long-haired adult in a bright pink suit steps out from the driver’s side, hair blown across their face. On the right, a woman in a vivid green outfit leans from the rear door with one arm extended in a dance pose. The city remains far below in the background.\n\nThe message changes to “BE CONFIDENT” in the same large white lettering. A dancer in green, with long dark hair and pink sleeves visible, stands near the front of the orange Cadillac holding two open white fans raised high, while the car’s grille and crest occupy the right side of the image.\n\nThe commercial ends on a still promotional layout at sunset. A white Cadillac sedan is parked on an elevated roadway or overlook with mountains and a warm orange-purple sky behind it. On the left are the Cadillac crest and the words “MOVE UP.” On the right, large lease text identifies a “2023 CT5 Premium Luxury AWD” and shows “$499 per month” for “39” months, with “$3,969 due at signing”